She looked at Quickstrike who was on the ground in pain.  She went to 
the lab and looked around.  She saw the viles that had the mind 
numbing liquid in it.  She had used it on Dracona.  It would do the 
same for Quickstrike.  It would stop the pain and hopefully make him 
feel better.  She grabbed a vile and a needle.  She filled the needle 
and walked over to Quickstrike.

"I have something that might take away the pain." she looked at him 
and wanted to help him.
"Please let me give this to you."
